--- !u!114 &386051687
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 386051686}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f0993e3529637bf44be01329bb9fddc6, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CookReyaNPC
  interactionRange: 5
  playerLayer:
    serializedVersion: 2
    m_Bits: 128
  dialogueBox: {fileID: 1668224383}
  textDisplay: {fileID: 1711400691}
  nameDisplay: {fileID: 1951556403}
  typeSpeed: 0.04
  movePoint: {fileID: 0}
  walkSpeed: 2
  rescueDialogue:
  - Thank you for saving me!
  - I am Cook Reya, the sub-chef of this STI College Caloocan.
  - You have to help us, my boss, the main chef, is corrupted!
  - Because of the corruption, he stole our entire rations for the month! Please
    get it back!
  questIncomplete:
  - Please defeat him first.
  questComplete:
  - "Cook Reya: Thank God you\u2019re back! Are you alright?"
  - "Yves: Yes Ma\u2019am, I am. Here\u2019s what I got after defeating the virus.
    I believe that these are yours."
  - 'Cook Reya: Thanks for your help! As a token of my appreciation, here''s the
    keycard for the faculty area! You can find a friend of mine that can help you! '
  - "Yves: There are more people on this campus? Isn\u2019t it dangerous?\r\n"
  - "???: Yup! But most of them are staying on the ground floor.. The building\u2019s
    corrupted. Some floors are safe.. I think.\r\n"
  - "Cook Reya: What do you mean? We can\u2019t really leave this place\u2026 at
    least not yet\u2026 [REDACTED] trapped all of us here- Anyways. My friend is
    also a staff member here. Tell them I sent you and they\u2019ll offer some help.
    \r\n"
  - "Yves: Okay, Thank you Ms. Reya. \r\n"
  - "Cook Reya: No problem kid. I hope you achieve whatever you need to do. This
    place isn\u2019t exactly the safest. I just wish none of this ever happened.
    \r\n"
  - 'Yves: Who is this [REDACTED]? Wow, I can''t even pronounce its name properly.

'
  - "???: You\u2019ll meet him.. Eventually.\r\n"
